REMI is a table game where 2 to 4 players play against each other to obtain the maximum of points. 
The results of each game are written down and summed up to determine the final winner.

This app automates the writing dow:
one screen where you enter the names of the players,
one screen where the results of each game are entered and elaborated by the app:
  maintain who's turn it is to start, remember atut and who closes and bring these into account, calculate total.
one screen to see the list of all the games up to this point.

The "How to2 document explais how to create your own project in Visual Studio Xamarin enviromnent and use is as you like.
The resulting app is for Android or iOs, the example generates the Android app.
